JTreeEx
public class DNDTree
extends javax.swing.JTree
implements java.awt.dnd.DropTargetListener, java.awt.dnd.DragSourceListener, java.awt.dnd.DragGestureListener

Creates a JTree with Drag and Drop facilities. Create and use an object of DNDTree instead of a JTree to include Drag and Drop features for your tree.
